author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents The Zawose Queens performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 05, 2024. 

Songs:
Intro  00:02
Kuseka  02:52
Duniya Hii  07:06
Maisha  12:18
Sauti Ya Mama 17:17

Pendo Zawose - Vocals, Illimba, Percussion
Leah Zawose - Vocals, Lllimba, Percussion
Ben Brown - Bass Synth, Electronics
Tal Janes - Guitar
Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Audio Mixer & Mastering Engineer: Julian Martlew

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
